Description: A fabulous new design, the Tweed Tote Bag ticks all the right boxes for a classic and practical everyday bag. Featuring a generous, roomy interior, with longer shoulder straps so the bag sits neatly under your arm, zipped enclosure, fully lined with internal mobile pouch and zipped pocket. Matching purse available to purchase. Dimensions: 27x39x14 cms Strap Measures 60 cms Earth Squared fairly traded bags & accessories are designed in the UK and handmande in Vietnam by a fairtrade certified organisation. Each purchase helps to create more work opportunities for other disadvantaged women and helps to change their lives and those of their families. Earth Squared is a registered member of BAFTS (British Association for Faitrade Shops & Suppliers). Additional Information If after browsing through our huge array of items you cannot find what you are looking for contact us. We will always go out of our way to source the product you are looking for. About Us MadMolly Trading is a small family business, offering quality gifts and homeware products to the whole family from 62 suppliers worldwide, with anything from funky keyrings to pop up 'Street Tennis' sets; from luxurious Bath House offerings to many fabulous garden and party buntings. The wooden toys are still a part of our range, in the form of Orange Tree Toys and Bajo, a new fabulous supplier based in Poland offering ingenious and strikingly colourful toys for smaller children. We sell across Europe and the Rest of the World as more people exploit the internet for shopping and postal systems improve, although the UK is the main market for us. We are trying our best on buying expeditions to reduce our dependence on China and to focus more on some talented and creative UK suppliers such as Just Slate Company & Linda MacDonald Jewellery. MadMolly's main ethos is superb customer service. We look after our customers as we would want to be treated ourselves, both pre and post purchase. Customers can call or e-mail us 7 days a week and we respond 7 days a week. Problems are rare, but we always resolve them to the customer's satisfaction. Many of our customers return time after time, like old friends. Shipping Information Once an order has been placed and paid for, it will be despatched within 1 working day. If the order is received by 2.30pm it will be despatched the same day. Within the UK, we use Royal Mail post for all deliveries with a value up to £50. Orders £50 are generally despatched via 48hour courier. We aim to keep all items in stock, but should an error occur we will contact you direct offering either a full refund, or give you an expected delivery date. International deliveries are sent either by Royal Mail International Signed For or Courier - both will need a signature on arrival as they are tracked from here to you. Next Day Delivery within UK We now offer next day delivery but can only guarantee it for orders placed before 12 noon (Mon - Thurs) to be delivered by noon the following day (Tues - Fri). If you require next day delivery after 12 noon we will do our utmost to help but cannot guarantee delivery. ReturnPolicy.Description:
Is there a purchase return guarantee?

If, for some reason, you are not satisfied with the product you ordered, you can send it back to us. Of course we would undertake the shipping cost in the case that it is the consequence of a mistake on our side. 	

Is it possible to swap the product? 
We will send you another product as soon as we receive the returned package.
We cover the postage cost of the second product in the case that it is due to a mistake on our side. If you change your mind about the product and return it to us, you will be asked to contribute to the product shipping costs. 								

Conditions of the returned product:
Please note that in order to receive a full refund of the product price, or an exchange of equal value, we will ask you to return the product in the same conditions as when we sent it to you.
